<item>
            <title>[FLINK-5307] Log configuration for every reporter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5307</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Mandatory properties, like host names or ports, generally lead to exceptions if they are wrongly configured. Optional properties however revert to default-values in case these properties are not configured at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logging all configured properties will make it easier to find typos/missing optional properties in the configuration.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
